    <item>
      <p>Color picker: Select the color to use within the edited image.</p>
    </item>
  </list>

  <p>The <link xref="selection_tools">selection tool</link> doesn't draw, but
  its capabilities are very powerful and useful for any image manipulation.</p>
  <p><link xref="canvas_tools">Other tools</link> allow you to transform the
  canvas or the selection.</p>

